{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "第四回“割鹿刀”主要讲述风四娘向萧十一郎讲述割鹿刀的来历：此刀乃当代铸剑名家徐鲁子耗尽心血铸造，取意“秦失其鹿，天下共逐，惟胜者得鹿而割之”，出炉不到半年却能砍断古代利器。割鹿刀正由赵无极、屠啸天、海灵子、司空曙四位高手护送入关。萧十一郎与风四娘在客栈相遇，风四娘试图激萧十一郎去夺刀，但萧十一郎以种种理由推脱。随后场景转到关外必经之路的市镇“恩德元”清真馆，老板马回回接待了四位护刀高手。赵无极温文和气，屠啸天豪迈，海灵子孤傲，司空曙则古怪凶狠，以鹰爪力活取牛心，震慑众人。四人在恩德元用餐，司空曙要求马回回找来当地著名的女子，等待过程中展现各自性格。本章通过对话和场景描写，引出割鹿刀这一关键物品，并初步刻画了四位护刀高手的形象。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "那把刀的故事，你不想听了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我不想听了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "为什么不想听？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "因为我若想听，你就不会说出来，我若不想听，你也许反而会忍不住要自动告诉我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你呀，你真是个鬼……别人常常说我是个女妖怪，但我这女妖怪遇见你这个鬼，也没法子了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "其实不管你想不想听，我都要告诉你的，那柄刀，叫\"割鹿刀\"！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "割鹿刀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不错，割鹿刀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "这名字倒新奇得很，我以前怎么从未听说过？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "因为这柄刀出炉还不到半年。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "一柄新铸成的刀，居然能砍断古代的利器？铸刀的这个人，功力难道能比得上春秋战国时那些名匠大师么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "继干将、莫邪、欧冶子等大师之后，还有位不出世的铸剑冶铁名家，你可知道是谁么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "莫非是徐夫人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不错，看不出你倒真有点学问。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "那柄割鹿刀莫非是徐鲁子徐大师铸成的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你也知道？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "徐鲁子乃徐夫人之嫡裔，你此刻忽然说起徐夫人，自然是和那柄\"割鹿刀\"有关系的了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不错，那柄'割鹿刀'确是徐大师所铸，为了这柄刀，他几乎已将毕生心血耗尽，这'割鹿'两字，取意乃是：'秦失其鹿，天下共逐，惟胜者得鹿而割之'。他的意思也就是惟有天下第一的英雄，才能得到这柄割鹿刀！他对这把刀的自豪，也就可想而知了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你自然是见过那柄刀的了。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "那的确是柄宝刀！'赤霞'遇见它，简直就好像变成了废铁。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "如此宝刀，不知我是否有缘一见！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你当然有机会能见到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我与徐大师素昧平生，他怎肯将如此宝刀轻易示人？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这柄刀现在已不在徐鲁子手里了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "在哪里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我也不知道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "想不到我也有让你着急的时候，到底还是年轻人沉不住气。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你说我是年轻人？我记得你还比我小两岁嘛。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "小鬼，少来拍老娘的马屁，我整整比你大五年四个月另三天，你本该乖乖的喊我一声大姐才是。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "大姐，你记得当真清楚得很。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "小老弟，还不快替大姐倒杯酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "是是是，倒酒！倒酒！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "哎——这才是我的乖小弟。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "那柄割鹿刀已在入关的道上了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "有没有人沿途护刀？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "如此宝刀，岂可无人护送？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "护刀入关的是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "赵无极……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "这赵无极可是那先天无极门的掌门人么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不是他是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "除了赵无极外，还有'关东大侠'屠啸天，海南剑派硕果仅存的惟一高手，'海灵子'……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "够了，就这三个人已够了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "但他们却认为还不够，所以又请了昔年独臂扫天山，单掌诛八寇的'独臂鹰王'司空曙。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "有这四人护刀入关，当今天下，只怕再也没有人敢去夺刀的了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "说来说去，原来你是想激我去替你夺刀。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你不敢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我替你夺刀，刀是你的，我还是一场空。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "他们护刀入关，你可知道是为了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "不知道，我也不想知道，反正他们也不会是为了要将刀送给我。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "就算你不敢去夺刀，难道也不想去见识见识么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "不想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我若是看到了那柄刀，就难免要心动，心动了就难免想去夺刀，夺不到就难免要送命。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "若是能夺到呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "若是夺到了，你就难免会问我要，我虽然舍不得，却又不好意思不给你，所以倒不如索性不去看的好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "原来你这样没出息，我真看错了你。好！你不去，我一个人去，没有你看我死不死得了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你这看见好东西就想要的脾气，真不知要到什么时候才能改得了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "speaker_name": "马回回",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "赵大侠远来辛苦了，请里面坐。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "text": "马掌柜的太客气了，请，请。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "speaker_name": "马回回",
      "listener": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "text": "屠老爷子，几年不见，你老人家身子越发的健朗了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "text": "这还不都是托朋友的福。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "speaker_name": "马回回",
      "listener": "char_hai_ling_zi",
      "text": "晚辈久慕海道长声名，今日得见，实在是三生有幸。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "海灵子",
      "listener": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "text": "好说，好说。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "speaker_name": "马回回",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "text": "听说老前辈要来，弟子特地选了条公牛……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "speaker_name": "司空曙",
      "listener": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "text": "公牛比母牛好，却不知是死的，还是活的？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "speaker_name": "马回回",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "text": "当然是活的，正留着给老前辈尝鲜哩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "speaker_name": "司空曙",
      "listener": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "text": "很好，很好，你这孙子总算还懂得孝敬我。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "text": "司空兄既已觉得满意了，为何还不动手？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "speaker_name": "司空曙",
      "listener": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "text": "你这糟老头子，又想看我老人家的把戏，是不是？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "speaker_name": "司空曙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来得好！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "speaker_name": "司空曙",
      "listener": "char_hai_ling_zi",
      "text": "你用不着皱眉头，就凭你，若想这么样吃颗活牛心，只怕还不太容易，你至少还得再苦练个十年八年的鹰爪力。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "海灵子",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "text": "我用不着练什么鹰爪力。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "speaker_name": "司空曙",
      "listener": "char_hai_ling_zi",
      "text": "你用不着练，难道你瞧不起我老爷子的鹰爪力？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "speaker_name": "司空曙",
      "listener": "char_hai_ling_zi",
      "text": "小杂毛，你用不着害怕，我老爷子只不过吓着你好玩的，我跟你那老杂毛师父是朋友，怎么能欺负你这小孩子。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "speaker_name": "马回回",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "菜虽不好，酒还不错，各位前辈请多喝两杯。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "speaker_name": "司空曙",
      "listener": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "text": "酒也不好。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "text": "酒虽是好酒，但若无红袖添酒，酒味也淡了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "speaker_name": "司空曙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "不错不错，到底还是你念过几天书，知道这\"酒\"字，和那\"色\"字是万万不能分开的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "speaker_name": "马回回",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "晚辈其实也已想到这一点，只怕此间的庸俗脂粉，入不了各位前辈的眼。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "speaker_name": "司空曙",
      "listener": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "text": "听说这里的女人很有名，难道连一个出色的都没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "speaker_name": "马回回",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "text": "出色的倒是有一个，但只有一个……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "speaker_name": "司空曙",
      "listener": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "text": "一个就已够了，这老杂毛是出家人，赵无极出名的怕老婆，屠老头已是心有余而力不足，你用不着替他们担心。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xiao_tian",
      "speaker_name": "屠啸天",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "text": "不错，你只要替司空前辈找到一个就成了，我这糟老头子只想在旁边瞧瞧。年纪大的人，只要瞧瞧就已经很过瘾了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无极",
      "listener": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "text": "怕老婆的人，还是连瞧都不要瞧的好。但若不瞧一眼，我还真不舍得走，马掌柜的，就烦你去走一趟吧。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "speaker_name": "马回回",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "text": "晚辈这就去找，只不过……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "speaker_name": "司空曙",
      "listener": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "text": "只不过怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "speaker_name": "马回回",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "text": "那位姑娘出名的架子大，未必一找就能找来。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "speaker_name": "司空曙",
      "listener": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "text": "那倒无妨，我就喜欢架子大的女人，架子大的女人必定有些与众不同，否则她的架子怎么大得起来？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "speaker_name": "马回回",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "text": "既是如此，就请前辈稍候……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_shu",
      "speaker_name": "司空曙",
      "listener": "char_ma_hui_hui",
      "text": "多等等也没关系，别的事我老爷子虽等不得，等女人的耐心我倒有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 396
    }
  ],
